annotationA: Probable phosphomannomutase; Involved in the synthesis of the GDP-mannose and dolichol-phosphate-mannose required for a number of critical mannosyl transfer reactions
annotationB: Hexokinase type 2; ATP binding; glucokinase activity; fructokinase activity; mannokinase activity; hexokinase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: glycolytic process; cellular glucose homeostasis
